Svelte and Solid both need a reactive accessor when query inputs can change.

```ts
// Svelte
const todos = new QuerySubscription(() =>
  projectId ? app.todos.where({ projectId }) : undefined,
);
```

```ts
// Solid
const todos = useAll(() => ({
  query: projectId() ? app.todos.where({ projectId: projectId() }) : undefined,
}));
```

Do not build the query once up front, because that captures stale inputs.

